GraphicCard.DescriptionField: Gigabyte GeForce RTX 4070 Ti EAGLE OC 12G is a powerful upper-midrange GPU with excellent 1440p and entry-level 4K gaming performance. Features triple-fan Windforce cooling and factory overclocking for better thermal and performance balance.

Gigabyte GeForce GTX 1660 SUPER OC 6G is a budget-friendly yet reliable GPU ideal for 1080p gaming. Known for its great price-to-performance ratio and low power consumption, making it suitable for entry-level and casual gamers.

Gigabyte Radeon RX 7900 XTX GAMING OC 24G is Flagship AMD-based graphics card designed for 4K gaming with ray tracing capabilities. Comes with massive 24GB VRAM and reinforced cooling for demanding workloads and gaming.
